data.description: Say hello to this gorgeous quarter of an acre, 3 bedroom, 2-bathroom property ready for a beautiful family to make it their home. Buit in 2020; It has granite countertops kitchen to enjoy a great meal. Low E insulated glass windows, weather stripping on all exterior doors, 30in flat panel kitchen cabinets; vinyl flooring' 50-gallon electric water heater, programmable smart thermostat, keyless smart locks, microwave, electric range, energy-efficient dishwasher, refrigerator, and 50-50 stainless steel kitchen sink. With a spacious 9' enclosed fenced back yard you will have the privacy to enjoy an outdoor get together or enjoy the fire pit.  This fantastic Texas home lets your family explore the best attractions of Fort Worth as its centric location is only 10min away from Downtown and a minute away from the main HWY, 287.
